        %h2 Your post, digitized.
        %p.lead Many Peace Corps posts struggle put themselves online. Maintaining a basic online presence is time-consuming. Distributing content online, editing content collaboratively, and fostering communities of learning can be a full-time job, and expensive.
      %p DigitalPost is an open-source, post-driven platform targeting just those challenges. With an out-of-the-box structure which matches the structure at your post, everything has a place. The interface is simple and intuitive, and it comes in local languages.
